":"2583f5d4ecaeee0ba77f124a0bd3a3fd99792928","tid":2204441,"uid":14918,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T05:15:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/tuckercarlson/status/1306053036448583680?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftuckercarlson%2Fstatus%2F1306053036448583680%3Fs%3D21&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvYdddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=4252e9e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftuckercarlson%2Fstatus%2F1306053036448583680%3Fs%3D21&h=cde35045\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/tuckercarlson/status/1306053036448583680?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁咪RT FOX NEWS既訪問囉<br />\nBam本人account仲有media"},{"pid":"10bd8cd66099a159464bf16db9d1c1d95a810cfb","tid":2204441,"uid":273218,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T05:17:02.000Z","msg":"閆博士指證既係中国共產黨，而且指證埋Bill Gates foundation等美國公司資助有關中共實驗室研究，這水太深，太污濁，涉及太多勢力，尤其報告挑戰左之前好多專家既睇法。<br />\n<br />\n本人昨晚亦大約睇左大部分有關報告中文版（原文由以下網站所翻譯簡體版）<br />\n<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/GlobalHimalaya/status/1305937893123219456\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2FGlobalHimalaya%2Fstatus%2F1305937893123219456&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvYdddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=fd774f91\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2FGlobalHimalaya%2Fstatus%2F1305937893123219456&h=6b1552b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/GlobalHimalaya/status/1305937893123219456</a><br />\n，大致係話中共用RaTG13呢隻有96%相似既病毒去誤導科學界，所有科學界圍爐認為病毒不會不是來自天然都係基於病毒來自RaTG13 既假設。<br />\n<br />\n但閆博士指出RaTG13有可能係虛構因為天然界從未出現過，而真正源頭其實係舟山蝙蝠病毒，我尋晚查返舊聞，原來袁國勇曾經好老實咁在本年一月爆左響口話病毒來自舟山蝙蝠病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，當時應該亦係聽左牆內比較正常既科學家所講，但後來據閆博士所講， 源頭來自舟山蝙蝠病毒講法好快被壓左落來。而1月時舟山蝙蝠病毒據報導相似度係88%,但據閆博士報告此病毒有一d高度機會突變既特徵，係跟武漢病毒係100%一致，所以武漢病毒非常不可能來自天然。<br />\n<br />\n另一點提到係，無人講過突變4%需要幾耐，但我睇幾個報導估計要幾十年以上，此為第二點<br />\n<br />\n另外，報告提及武漢病毒必定係合成病毒，必家有中間宿主，但到現在仍未搵到有關宿主。"},{"pid":"0cbe6cc6a7a40aa4ebecaa4defbee5ebd5ac5d36","tid":2204441,"uid":144626,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T05:18:18.000Z","msg":"呢個真係義士中嘅義士<br />\n玩命走黎踢爆"},{"pid":"e4cfe89f7800ee6101a0b58c087ef309a409b991","tid":2204441,"uid":98551,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0cbe6cc6a7a40aa4ebecaa4defbee5ebd5ac5d36","tid":2204441,"uid":144626,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T05:18:18.000Z","msg":"呢個真係義士中嘅義士<br />\n玩命走黎踢爆"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T05:20:28.000Z","msg":"應該唔係得佢一個走去美國<br />\n只不過得佢一個有命去到"},{"pid":"fe50f405eb5d9761b2c4266298cc6162090fbc6a","tid":2204441,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4cfe89f7800ee6101a0b58c087ef309a409b991","tid":2204441,"uid":98551,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0cbe6cc6a7a40aa4ebecaa4defbee5ebd5ac5d36","tid":2204441,"uid":144626,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T05:18:18.000Z","msg":"呢個真係義士中嘅義士<br />\n玩命走黎踢爆"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T05:20:28.000Z","msg":"應該唔係得佢一個走去美國<br />\n只不過得佢一個有命去到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T05:21:38.000Z","msg":"所以呢班友真係好勇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以一己之力硬拼強國"},{"pid":"99153eb9d53b64b6c05430168ff7000b660ccb2a","tid":2204441,"uid":98551,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"fe50f405eb5d9761b2c4266298cc6162090fbc6a","tid":2204441,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4cfe89f7800ee6101a0b58c087ef309a409b991","tid":2204441,"uid":98551,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0cbe6cc6a7a40aa4ebecaa4defbee5ebd5ac5d36","tid":2204441,"uid":144626,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T05:18:18.000Z","msg":"呢個真係義士中嘅義士<br />\n玩命走黎踢爆"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020